CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 30, 1958, pg. 32 reads: "...annual United Golfers Association tournament being played at North Park this week.."
TitMainTitle: Four male golfers, including man on right wearing light colored pants, button down short sleeved collared shirt with graphic print, eyeglasses, and cap, crouched down holding outstretched putters toward hole, gathered on North Park golf course for UGA tournament
